1
00:00:03,537 --> 00:00:08,376
(Minseok) ⟨I was chased out of a South Korean chaebol family after being accused of embezzlement→

2
00:00:08,442 --> 00:00:12,880
In despair, I met Momoko, a doctor at the clinic⟩

3
00:00:12,947 --> 00:00:14,882
⟨For me, Momoko is →

4
00:00:14,949 --> 00:00:16,884
He became an important person...⟩

5
00:00:16,951 --> 00:00:18,886
(Kyoko) I'm sure Momoko too →

6
00:00:18,953 --> 00:00:21,889
I'm sure Taku-chan and I can make a good family.

7
00:00:21,956 --> 00:00:24,392
(Takuto) I confess to Momoko.

8
00:00:24,458 --> 00:00:27,395
(Minseok) ⟨I can't make her happy...⟩

9
00:00:27,461 --> 00:00:29,397
(Takuto) Don't just say nice things.

10
00:00:29,463 --> 00:00:31,899
(Minseok) ⟨But...⟩ (Kazami) You gave me a gift for leaving the hospital.

11
00:00:31,966 --> 00:00:33,901
I'll use it as a talisman.

12
00:00:33,968 --> 00:00:36,904
Minseok-kun made Momo-chan smile.

13
00:00:36,971 --> 00:00:40,908
(Minseok) ⟨I just couldn't stop my feelings for Momoko⟩

14
00:00:40,975 --> 00:00:43,411
I will do my best to make you smile again.

15
00:00:43,477 --> 00:00:45,413
Momoko-san.

16
00:00:45,479 --> 00:00:47,415
I like it.

17
00:00:47,481 --> 00:00:50,918
(Momoko) I love you too.

18
00:00:50,985 --> 00:01:05,433
♪～

19
00:01:32,960 --> 00:01:34,895
(In a whisper) Minseok-san.

20
00:01:34,962 --> 00:01:46,907
♪～

21
00:01:46,974 --> 00:01:49,910
(Momoko) Huh?

22
00:01:49,977 --> 00:01:51,912
(Minseok) Good morning.

23
00:01:51,979 --> 00:01:53,914
(Momoko) Were you awake?

24
00:01:53,981 --> 00:01:57,985
(Minseok) I kept quiet because it was cute.

25
00:02:00,988 --> 00:02:02,990
(Momoko) Already.

26
00:02:06,927 --> 00:02:08,929
(Momoko) Green onions.

27
00:02:15,936 --> 00:02:20,941
(Minseok) I am raising them with care.

28
00:02:24,945 --> 00:02:26,947
(Momoko) Thank you.

29
00:02:28,949 --> 00:02:31,385
Ah.

30
00:02:31,452 --> 00:02:34,388
Komawo.

31
00:02:34,455 --> 00:02:35,890
(Minseok) Huh?

32
00:02:35,956 --> 00:02:38,893
(Momoko) I learned a little bit of Korean.

33
00:02:38,959 --> 00:02:44,899
>> Korean

34
00:02:44,965 --> 00:02:46,400
(Momoko) Huh?

35
00:02:46,467 --> 00:02:50,971
(Minseok) ``There is no tree that will not fall even after being cut 10 times.''

36
00:02:53,474 --> 00:02:55,910
To Momoko →

37
00:02:55,976 --> 00:02:58,412
The words that made me meet again.

38
00:02:58,479 --> 00:03:00,414
(Momoko) Yeorubong…｡

39
00:03:00,481 --> 00:03:02,416
>> Korean

40
00:03:02,483 --> 00:03:04,351
(Momoko) Yorubon Ichigo.

41
00:03:04,418 --> 00:03:06,353
>> Korean

42
00:03:06,420 --> 00:03:08,355
(Momoko) Ahn nomoganun.

43
00:03:08,422 --> 00:03:10,357
>> Korean

44
00:03:10,424 --> 00:03:12,860
(Momoko) Nam Otta.

45
00:03:12,927 --> 00:03:14,929
Woohoo!

46
00:03:19,934 --> 00:03:21,368
(sound of door opening)

47
00:03:21,435 --> 00:03:24,872
(Momoko) Huh? Wait, what time is it now?

48
00:03:24,939 --> 00:03:26,373
(Minseok) It's 8 o'clock.

49
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:29,376
(Momoko) 8 o'clock is dangerous 8 o'clock is dangerous!

50
00:03:29,443 --> 00:03:34,882
(Sound of keyboard hitting)

51
00:03:34,949 --> 00:03:36,884
(sound of door closing)

52
00:03:36,951 --> 00:03:38,886
