53
00:03:38,953 --> 00:03:40,955
(Minseok) Good morning.

54
00:03:42,957 --> 00:03:44,892
You're early.

55
00:03:44,959 --> 00:03:48,395
>> Morning routine? Even though she looks like this, she's a nurse.

56
00:03:48,462 --> 00:03:50,464
(Minseok) Ah~｡

57
00:03:57,972 --> 00:04:00,407
