58
00:04:00,474 --> 00:04:04,345
The tree in the courtyard is beautiful, isn't it?

59
00:04:04,411 --> 00:04:06,847
>> Huh?

60
00:04:06,914 --> 00:04:10,851
(Minseok) Ah, is that tree quite difficult to take care of?

61
00:04:10,918 --> 00:04:12,353
>>Which one?

62
00:04:12,419 --> 00:04:14,855
(Minseok) That's it. >> Huh?

63
00:04:14,922 --> 00:04:17,858
(Minseok) This, this... what's ahead. >> What's next?

64
00:04:17,925 --> 00:04:20,861
(Minseok) Ah... It's beyond that. It's beyond that. >> Beyond?

65
00:04:20,928 --> 00:04:22,863
Huh? Is that it?

66
00:04:22,930 --> 00:04:24,865
Eh, which one? (Minseok) Oh!

67
00:04:24,932 --> 00:04:26,867
It's beyond that.

68
00:04:26,934 --> 00:04:28,869
>> What's next? (Minseok) Yes.

69
00:04:28,936 --> 00:04:32,373
>>It seems like it can grow anywhere.

70
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:36,877
By the way, I've never taken care of it.

71
00:04:36,944 --> 00:04:38,879
(Minseok) Is that so?

72
00:04:38,946 --> 00:04:41,382
>> But it blooms like that.

73
00:04:41,448 --> 00:04:42,883
(Momoko) Wow, ah!

74
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:45,386
>> Ah, Momo-chan, good morning.

75
00:04:45,452 --> 00:04:47,388
(Momoko) Good morning. >> Where are you going?

76
00:04:47,454 --> 00:04:49,390
(Momoko) No, I just arrived.

77
00:04:49,456 --> 00:04:51,892
I was worried that I had locked the door in the house, so I thought I should go back.

78
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:53,394
>> Huh?

79
00:04:53,460 --> 00:04:55,396
(Momoko) It's okay, I locked it.

80
00:04:55,462 --> 00:04:57,398
The key, the house key. (Kazami) Oh, that's right.

81
00:04:57,464 --> 00:04:59,400
Good morning. (Minseok) Good morning.

82
00:04:59,466 --> 00:05:01,902
(Kazami) Ah, good morning. (Momoko) Minseok-san.

83
00:05:01,969 --> 00:05:03,837
good morning.

84
00:05:03,904 --> 00:05:07,841
(Minseok) Good morning, Momoko-sensei.

85
00:05:07,908 --> 00:05:22,423
♪～

86
00:05:25,225 --> 00:05:27,928
(Female) Wow, so beautiful.

87
00:05:27,995 --> 00:05:30,664
(Minseok) Welcome.

88
00:05:30,931 --> 00:05:34,802
(Female) I've always wanted to stay there.

89
00:05:34,868 --> 00:05:36,870
Hey Tomo-kun.

90
00:05:38,872 --> 00:05:40,808
(Female) Tomo-kun.

91
00:05:40,874 --> 00:05:44,311
(Kusano) Ah, ah…｡

92
00:05:44,378 --> 00:05:46,814
Ah, sorry.

93
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:49,316
