94
00:05:49,383 --> 00:05:51,819
(Kusano) Please check in.

95
00:05:51,885 --> 00:05:54,321
(Staff) Dear Kashikomari, may I ask your name?

96
00:05:54,388 --> 00:05:57,825
Ah, this is Tomoyuki Kusano.

97
00:05:57,891 --> 00:06:00,327
(Staff) Are you coming by car? >> Yes.

98
00:06:00,394 --> 00:06:02,329
(Staff) We will keep your parking ticket.

99
00:06:02,396 --> 00:06:06,266
Ah... Parking ticket Ah, yes, yes...｡

100
00:06:06,333 --> 00:06:08,836
(Sound of a box falling) (Staff) I'll keep it for you.

101
00:06:11,839 --> 00:06:15,776
Customer, this has been dropped.

102
00:06:15,843 --> 00:06:18,278
Ah, ah…｡

103
00:06:18,345 --> 00:06:20,781
what happened? >> Ah... uh...｡

104
00:06:20,848 --> 00:06:23,784
(Minseok) It looks like a key to your home.

105
00:06:23,851 --> 00:06:27,287
>> It's a key... It's a key.

106
00:06:27,354 --> 00:06:29,289
It's the key.

107
00:06:29,356 --> 00:06:33,293
I'll get rid of that kind of thing soon.

108
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,362
(Minseok) Please take your time.

109
00:06:38,365 --> 00:06:40,801
(Staff) Now, I'll give it back to you.

110
00:06:40,868 --> 00:06:42,803
(Minseok's voice) Thank you for your hard work.

111
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:45,372
(Natsume) Deputy Manager, thank you for your hard work.

112
00:06:49,376 --> 00:06:58,318
(sound of washing hands)

113
00:06:58,385 --> 00:07:00,387
>> About today.

114
00:07:02,389 --> 00:07:04,258
(Minseok) Yes.

115
00:07:04,324 --> 00:07:06,760
>> It wasn't a bad follow up.

116
00:07:06,827 --> 00:07:08,762
(Minseok) Eh.

117
00:07:08,829 --> 00:07:19,273
♪～

118
00:07:19,339 --> 00:07:21,775
>> That's all.

119
00:07:21,842 --> 00:07:23,844
I don't know.

120
00:07:27,848 --> 00:07:31,285
(Natsume) The manager was praising you just now.

121
00:07:31,351 --> 00:07:34,788
``The assistant manager just saw the ring box that the customer dropped →

122
00:07:34,855 --> 00:07:38,292
When I noticed his plan to propose, I used my wits.

123
00:07:38,358 --> 00:07:40,794
Please follow my example.''

124
00:07:40,861 --> 00:07:45,799
(Minseok) No, there are many customers who plan to propose at the hotel.

125
00:07:45,866 --> 00:07:49,803
>> However, as soon as the deputy manager came in, he acted cold.

126
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:53,307
She had a face like that of a tsundere.

127
00:07:53,373 --> 00:08:02,816
♪～

128
00:08:02,883 --> 00:08:04,251
