131
00:08:08,822 --> 00:08:10,257
(Minseok) Ah...

132
00:08:10,324 --> 00:08:13,260
(Takuto) No, no, let's stop being that awkward.

133
00:08:13,327 --> 00:08:15,262
(Minseok) Sorry.

134
00:08:15,329 --> 00:08:17,764
(Takuto) Why did you apologize?

135
00:08:17,831 --> 00:08:20,767
As long as Mincheok runs to see Momoko →

136
00:08:20,834 --> 00:08:23,770
I guess I deserve to lose too.

137
00:08:23,837 --> 00:08:25,772
(Minseok) Huh?

138
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:27,341
(Takuto) Hmm.

139
00:08:35,349 --> 00:08:37,784
(Minseok) Wow! (Takuto) Let's go!

140
00:08:37,851 --> 00:08:40,287
Okay! (Minseok) Hey, hey…｡

141
00:08:40,354 --> 00:08:42,289
(Takuto) I'm home. (Minseok) I'm home.

142
00:08:42,356 --> 00:08:45,792
(Children) Welcome back. (Minseok) I'm home.

143
00:08:45,859 --> 00:08:48,295
(Takuto) Okay, I'm home.

144
00:08:48,362 --> 00:08:49,796
(Momoko) Oh.

145
00:08:49,863 --> 00:08:51,298
(Takuto) No, no, that's it→

146
00:08:51,365 --> 00:08:54,368
"Why aren't you home right now?"

147
00:08:55,869 --> 00:08:58,805
(Momoko) That's right. (Child) Takuto This way, this way.

148
00:08:58,872 --> 00:09:01,375
(Takuto) That's why I'm not calling you that anymore.

149
00:09:04,311 --> 00:09:06,813
(Minseok) I'm home. (Momoko) Welcome back.

150
00:09:08,815 --> 00:09:11,752
>> Alright!

151
00:09:11,818 --> 00:09:14,755
(Momoko) After eating, clean up the dishes before playing.

152
00:09:14,821 --> 00:09:16,823
>> Yes.

153
00:09:18,825 --> 00:09:20,761
(Yusuke) Haru-kun is normal.

154
00:09:20,827 --> 00:09:22,763
(Takuto) Oh, that's good.

155
00:09:22,829 --> 00:09:24,264
>> What do you think?

156
00:09:24,331 --> 00:09:26,767
Mika-chan is normal. >> Thank you.

157
00:09:26,833 --> 00:09:28,769
(Takuto) Please check me out too. (Yusuke) Yeah.

158
00:09:28,835 --> 00:09:32,272
(Mika) What do you think? (Yusuke) Takuto Normal.

159
00:09:32,339 --> 00:09:34,841
lip sync

160
00:09:37,344 --> 00:09:39,846
lip sync

161
00:09:43,850 --> 00:09:49,356
lip sync

162
