Momo-chan-sensei is abnormal!

163
00:09:58,365 --> 00:10:01,301
(Momoko) Huh? >> Something is wrong, my heart is pounding!

164
00:10:01,368 --> 00:10:03,303
Isn't your face red?

165
00:10:03,370 --> 00:10:05,806
(Momoko) It's not red.

166
