>> Do you want to measure your temperature? (Momoko) It's okay, it's normal, it's normal.

167
00:10:09,376 --> 00:10:11,812
>> Your face is turning red! (Momoko) It's not red!

168
00:10:11,878 --> 00:10:14,314
Thank you for the meal.

169
00:10:14,381 --> 00:10:17,818
(Yusuke) My heart was pounding, my heart was pounding.

170
00:10:17,884 --> 00:10:20,821
(Momoko) Yes, please. (Minseok) Thank you.

171
00:10:20,887 --> 00:10:23,824
(Takuto) Okay, then I guess it's time to go home.

172
00:10:23,890 --> 00:10:25,826
