173
00:10:25,892 --> 00:10:28,328
(Takuto) The secret to being handsome is sleep.

174
00:10:28,395 --> 00:10:30,831
Okay, I'll send them all.

175
00:10:30,897 --> 00:10:32,833
People from the same direction, get together.

176
00:10:32,899 --> 00:10:34,835
>> Yes.

177
00:10:34,901 --> 00:10:38,839
Tatsuru: Since we're close, do you want to go home with me?

178
00:10:38,905 --> 00:10:40,841
(Tatsuru) I'll eat some more.

179
00:10:40,907 --> 00:10:43,844
(Tatsuru) Director, you can go home first.

180
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:47,347
(Momoko) Ah, that's fine. Director, I'm on duty to clean up, so I'll stay behind.

181
00:10:47,414 --> 00:10:49,349
(Kazami) Oh, really? (Momoko) Yes.

182
00:10:49,416 --> 00:10:52,352
(Kazami) Well then, you're spoiled for words. (Momoko) Yes.

183
00:10:52,419 --> 00:10:54,421
(Kazami) Go ahead. (Minseok) Take care.

184
00:10:55,922 --> 00:10:57,858
(Momoko) Yes, everyone please be careful.

185
00:10:57,924 --> 00:11:00,360
(All) Bye-bye! (Momoko) Good night.

186
00:11:00,427 --> 00:11:02,362
Good night.

187
00:11:02,429 --> 00:11:05,365
(Minseok) Oh, it's almost there.

188
00:11:06,867 --> 00:11:09,302
>>I don't want to eat it.

189
00:11:09,369 --> 00:11:11,872
(Minseok) Are you full?

190
00:11:14,374 --> 00:11:17,310
>>I don't want to go home.

191
00:11:17,377 --> 00:11:19,813
(Momoko) Tatsuru Is Mommy late today?

192
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:21,815
>>Yes.

193
00:11:21,882 --> 00:11:26,319
I'm home alone because I'm scared.

194
00:11:26,386 --> 00:11:28,321
(Minseok) I see.

195
00:11:28,388 --> 00:11:31,825
Well then, shall I stay here with you until mom comes back?

196
00:11:31,892 --> 00:11:33,827
>> Is it okay? (Minseok) Yes.

197
00:11:33,894 --> 00:11:36,329
(Momoko) Then I'll call Tatsuru's mom.

198
00:11:36,396 --> 00:11:37,831
(Minseok) Sorry.

199
00:11:37,898 --> 00:11:39,332
>>Thank you!

200
00:11:39,399 --> 00:11:40,834
(Minseok) Ah.

201
00:11:40,901 --> 00:11:42,836
(Tatsuru) Minseok-san, let's play.

202
00:11:42,903 --> 00:11:44,838
(Minseok) Well, after you finish eating this. (Tatsuru) Yeah.

203
00:11:44,905 --> 00:11:47,340
Thank you very much for today.

204
00:11:47,407 --> 00:11:49,843
(Momoko) No, not at all. >> See you soon!

205
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:51,845
(Minseok) Good night. (Momoko) Bye bye.

206
00:11:51,912 --> 00:11:53,914
(Mother) Excuse me.

207
00:11:55,916 --> 00:11:59,853
(Momoko) Tatsuru: Minseok-san was all to himself and was excited.

208
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:03,356
(Minseok) I was the one who played with it. (Momoko) Woohoo.

209
00:12:03,423 --> 00:12:07,360
Wow, so beautiful.

210
00:12:10,363 --> 00:12:12,799
>> Korean

211
